special_powers.name: BURNING TRAIL
special_powers.description: When Firewing Pegasus moves dues to its own action, after actions resolve it can use Smoke Cloud as a free action, but when it does, it may only place terrain markers in squares it moved through.

special_powers.name: BUG EYES
special_powers.description: Kamakiriman can use Super Senses and Toughness.

special_powers.name: WARRIORS ARE WEAK
special_powers.description: When Kinetic Soldier targets a character that can use Blades/Claws/Fangs or Charge with an attack, modify Kinetic Soldier's attack and damage values by +1.

special_powers.name: MOTHERLY PROTECTION
special_powers.description: Mother Grizzly and adjacent friendly characters can use Toughness.

special_powers.name: NUISANCE
special_powers.description: When Neko Mane King takes damage from an attack, after actions resolve, characters on the attacker's force can't be given actions until that player's next turn.

special_powers.name: NO ESCAPE
special_powers.description: Neko Mane King can use Phasing/Teleport and Plasticity.

special_powers.name: SELFLESSNESS
special_powers.description: Adjacent friendly characters can use Regeneration.  When they use it in this way, choose a number 1-6 as the minimum result for the d6 roll and, after actions resolve, deal The Forgiving Maiden that much unavoidable damage.

special_powers.name: MULTIPLE ARMS
special_powers.description: Give Asura Priest a double power action.  Asura Priest can immediately make four close combat attacks as free actions, but can't target the same character with more than two attacks.

special_powers.name: DAGGERS OF DEMISE
special_powers.description: Once per game, give Asura Priest a ranged combat action even if it is adjacent to an opposing character.  Make a ranged combat attack with an area of effect targeting each opposing character within 6 squares and line of fire.  For each hit character, roll a d6 and deal that character that much damage.

special_powers.name: I STAND ALONE
special_powers.description: If Blade Knight is the only friendly character on the map, modify his combat values by +1 and if he can use Toughness, he can use Invulnerability instead.

special_powers.name: COUNTER SPELL
special_powers.description: Breaker the Magical Warrior begins the game with a Spell token on this card. While the Spell token is on this card, he can use Super Senses. Give Breaker the Magical Warrior a power action and remove the Spell token to deal 2 penetrating damage to an opposing character within 6 squares and line of fire. -or- Give Breaker the Magical Warrior a free action and remove the Spell token to deal 1 penetrating damage to an opposing character within 6 squares and line of fire.

special_powers.name: CANNON FIRE
special_powers.description: Cannon Soldier can use Telekinesis, but may only place adjacent friendly characters.  When it does, its line of fire isn't blocked by the placed character and, after actions resolve, it may make a ranged combat attack as a free action with an area of effect targeting all opposing characters adjacent to the placed character.  Hit characters are each dealt 2 damage.

special_powers.name: FIENDISH SUPPORT
special_powers.description: When Sangan would be KO'd, remove all action tokens from up to 3 adjacent friendly characters whose total point value is 150 or less.

special_powers.name: DRAGONIC CONTROL
special_powers.description: Dragon Piper can use Mind Control. When it does, characters it targets that have a printed damage value of 3 or more modify their defense value by -3 this turn and it takes no damage due to the point value of characters with the word Dragon in their name.

name: La Jinn the Mystical Genie of the Lamp

special_powers.name: HIDING IN THE LAMP
special_powers.description: Each time La Jinn the Mystical Genie of the Lamp is hit by an attack and that attack resolves, he modifies his defense value by +2 until your next turn.

special_powers.name: WHIRLWIND OF WEAPONS
special_powers.description: Mechanicalchaser can use Charge and Flurry.

special_powers.name: TACTICAL MOVEMENT
special_powers.description: Once per game, when Morphing Jar is hit with an attack, after actions resolve, starting with you, each player chooses a friendly character and places it into an opponent's starting area unitl all characters have been placed.

special_powers.name: WHAT DOESN'T IT SEE?
special_powers.description: Morphing Jar can use Perplex and Probability Control.

special_powers.name: FUSION
special_powers.description: When a listed character is adjacent to all other listed characters and hits an opposing character, after actions resolve it may be given a free action to replace these characters with Alligator's Sword Dragon from your sideline. When Alligator's Sword Dragon enters the game in this way, it starts the same number of clicks from it's starting line as the character given the action and modifies its combat values by +1. This trait is active even when this character is not on the map. Alligator's Sword Baby Dragon

special_powers.name: SPELL: SWORDS OF REVEALING LIGHT
special_powers.description: Give the set character a power action and friendly characters can't be targeted by attacks until your next turn. At the beginning of your next turn, remove the spell.

special_powers.name: TRAP: CRUSH CARD VIRUS
special_powers.description: When the set character is KO'd, after actions resolve you may activate this trap. Deal 1 unavoidable damage to each opposing character of 150 or more points within 6 squares of the square the set character last occupied. Remove the trap.

special_powers.name: FIRE SPLASH
special_powers.description: Baby Dragon can use Energy Explosion and Penetrating/Psychic Blast.

special_powers.name: EMBRACE THE DARKNESS
special_powers.description: Castle of Dark Illusions can use Stealth.  Castle of Dark Illusions can use Smoke Cloud as a free action but, when it does, hindering terrain markers must be placed within 1 square of Castle of Dark Illusions.

special_powers.name: AN ARMY WITHIN
special_powers.description: When Castle of Dark Illusions uses the Carry ability, it may carry 3 characters normally or it may carry 1 character regardless of its combat symbols.

special_powers.name: TRAP/SPELL
special_powers.description: When this character is KO'd or when building your force by paying the purple point cost, add this dial face down to your Trap/Spell pool. Give a friendly Yu-Gi-Oh! character a power action to set this dial from your pool by choosing "Spell Symbol" or "Trap Symbol" and placing it face down on their card. The set character may use the effects of that Trap/Spell.

special_powers.name: SPELL: CHANGE OF HEART
special_powers.description: Give the set character a free action.  The set character can use Mind Control this turn.  When it does, modify its attack value by +2 and, after actions resolve, remove the spell.

special_powers.name: TRAP: TRAP HOLE
special_powers.description: When an opposing character moves through a square within 4 squares of the set character, after actions resolve, you may activate this trap.  Give that character 1 action token, or deal them 1 unavoidable damage if they already have 2 action tokens, then remove the trap.

special_powers.name: LAUNCH CATAPULT
special_powers.description: Catapult Turtle can use Telekinesis, but may only use it to place adjacent friendly characters with a lower point value.  When it does, after actions resolve, that character may make a close or ranged combat attack as a free action.

special_powers.name: TIDAL SHIELD
special_powers.description: Once per turn, if Suijin is adjacent to a friendly character that's the only character of an attack, you may give Suijin an action token. If you do, that attack targets Suijin even if it is otherwise an illegal target.

special_powers.name: WATER DEFENSE
special_powers.description: At the beginning of your turn, choose any number of adjacent friendly characters. Until your next turn, chosen characters decrease their attack values and increase their defense values by the number of action tokens on them.

special_powers.name: SALAMANDRA FLAMESTRIKE
special_powers.description: Flame Swordsman can use Charge and Sidestep.

special_powers.name: FLAMING SWORD OF BATTLE
special_powers.description: Flame Swordsman can use Blades/Claws/Fangs and Poison. When he uses Blades/Claws/Fangs and rolls a 5-6 for damage, after actions resolve, all damage dealt to the hit character is increased by 1 until your next turn.

special_powers.name: SPIRAL SHAVER

special_powers.name: DEFENSIVE FORMATION
special_powers.description: Once per game, when Kazejin or an adjacent friendly character is dealt damage from an attack, you may give Kazejin an action token. If you do, that character ignores all damage from the attack.

special_powers.name: SQUALL BARRICADE

special_powers.name: THUNDER STRIKE ATTACK

When you do, KO that character and place Relinquished on his starting click in a square that character occupied.

special_powers.name: HYPNOTIC ATTRACTION
special_powers.description: Relinquished can use Steal Energy. When Relinquished hits an opposing character, give that character an Absorption token if it doesn't already have one. Characters with an Absorption token modify their combat values by -1 if not already modified by this effect. Modify Relinquished's combat values by +1 for every 2 Absorption tokens on opposing characters on the map.

special_powers.name: TIME MAGIC

special_powers.description: When the set character takes damage from an opponent's attack and is not KO'd, after actions resolve, you may activate this trap. Deal unavoidable damage to the attacking character equal to half the damage taken. Remove the trap.

special_powers.description: When the set character would be KO'd, instead roll a d6 that can't be rerolled.  On a result of 1-4, the character is KO'd normally.  On a result of 5, return it to your starting area on its last non-KO click.  On a result of 6, return it to any starting area on its last non-KO click, then heal 1 damage.  Remove the trap.

special_powers.name: WHITE LIGHTNING
special_powers.description: Blue-Eyes White Dragon can use Penetrating/Psychic Blast and Pulse Wave.  When it uses either, hit characters are given an action token and any that can't be given an action token are dealt 1 penetrating damage after actions resolve.

special_powers.name: INFERNO FIRE BLAST
special_powers.description: Red-Eyes B. Dragon can use Energy Explosion and Penetrating/Psychic Blast. When it uses either, after actions resolve, hit characters are knocked back equal to the damage taken.

special_powers.name: SHARP CLAWS
special_powers.description: When Red-Eyes B. Dragon is targeted with an attack by an opposing character 150 points or less, after the attack resolves, modify Red-Eyes B. Dragon's combat values by +1 until the end of your next turn.

special_powers.name: MYSTIC BOX

special_powers.description: Give Dark Magician a free action and choose two standard attack powers. Dark Magician can use those powers until end of turn.

The "Set" character may use the effects of that Trap/Spell.

special_powers.name: SPELL: RING OF MAGNETISM
special_powers.description: Give the Set character a power action and modify its defense value by -2. When an opposing character targets a friendly character that is not the Set character with an attack, modify the attacker's attack value by -2. When the Set character takes damage, this spell is removed from play.

special_powers.name: TRAP: SPELLBINDING CIRCLE
special_powers.description: When an opposing character with a higher point value hits the Set character with an attack, you may activate this trap. The attack is evaded and this trap is placed on the attacking character's card. A character with this trap on its card modifies its damage value by -1. Give a character with this trap on its card a power action and remove this trap from the game.

special_powers.name: LIGHTNING FAST
